  <scopecontent id="aspace_f6886bd474f2b2d5eb01a9c2a0ee3a4b">
    <head>COLLECTION DESCRIPTION</head>
<p>Correspondence, manuscripts of articles, genealogical notes, clippings, and photographs pertaining to Reed's secretaryship of the Hobasco Masonic Lodge in Ithaca, New York; other correspondence pertains to the early history of Cornell University, and the city of Ithaca; also, genealogical material pertaining to the Stevenson and Dumont families.</p>  </scopecontent>
